data.title: Another 48 Hrs.
data.meta_description: Where to watch Another 48 Hrs. (1990) starring Eddie Murphy, Nick Nolte, Brion James and directed by Walter Hill.
data.text: For the past four years, San Francisco cop Jack Cates has been after an unidentified drug kingpin who calls himself the Ice Man. Jack finds a picture that proves that the Ice Man has put a price on the head of Reggie Hammond, who is scheduled to be released from prison on the next day.
